snippet.title: TEKKEN 8 - RELEASE DATE AND EXCLUSIVE CONTENT REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Get ready, warriors.

The next King of Iron Fist tournament will start on January 26, 2024 👊
And there's so much more to catch in the #TEKKEN8 Gamescom trailer 🥊

Learn more: https://tekken.com/purchase
